TOPPINGS: CHEESE: LOW MOISTURE PART SKIM MOZZARELLA CHEESE (PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES). SAUSAGE: PORK, WATER, SPICES, SALT, DEXTROSE, GARLIC POWDER, PAPRIKA. GRILLED SEASONED HAMBURGER;: BEEF, SALT, SPICES, FLAVORINGS, HYDROLYZED CORN PROTEIN, GRILL FLAVOR (MALTODEXTRIN, FLAVOR [FROM CORN OIL], MODIFIED CORN STARCH, CORN SYRUP SOLIDS. PEPPERONI: (PORK, BEEF, SALT, DEXTROSE, SODIUM NITRITE, BHA, BHT, CITRIC ACID, MAY CONTAIN WATER, SPICES, FLAVORING, SMOKE FLAVORING, PAPRIKA, OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE, SODIUM ASCORBATE, GARLIC POWDER, DEHYDRATED GARLIC). COOKED CAPICOLA: CHOPPED AND FORMED PORK SHOULDER BUTT, WATER, SALT, BROWN SUGAR, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, PAPRIKA, GARLIC, PEPPER, CHEYENNE PEPPER, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE. ASIAGO: (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT AND ENZYMES), POWDERED CELLULOSE (TO PREVENT CAKING). MINCED GARLIC. PARSLEY. SPICE BLEND: SPICES, (OREGANO, PEPPER, BASIL), MALTODEXTRIN, ONION & GARLIC, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL, PARSLEY.
